    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver. The exterior shows some visible wear, including several scratches and minor dings consistent with its age, and the interior has some staining and signs of use. Mechanically, it is sound and runs reliably, though it may require some routine maintenance in the near future to keep it in top shape. It's a solid choice for someone looking for functional transportation at a reasonable price.",
