    },
    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Looking for a rewarding project? This vehicle is ready for a dedicated owner to give it the TLC it needs! While it currently requires significant mechanical work and shows its age, it offers a great foundation for someone handy with a wrench or looking for a budget-friendly parts car. Grab this opportunity to bring a classic back to the road!",
